/api/sovereign-recognition/   /.netlify/functions/sovereign-recognition    200
/api/identity-reset           /.netlify/functions/identity-reset          200
/api/identity-reset/          /.netlify/functions/identity-reset           200
# Device binding (Face + Passkey) — required for "Bind device" step
/api/v1/save-pillars-at-75    /.netlify/functions/save-pillars-at-75    200
